{"tid":1857642,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"兵臨城下！支那肺炎殺到支那中南海","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T10:53:21.000Z","uid":32511,"like":94,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"7238949a5093d1eca5cc7cf50de4e99e70d481b7","tid":1857642,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"新消息：北京市西城區留學路一商戶的兒媳，臘月二十八從武漢返回，昨天開始發燒隔離，目前整條街封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n周圍是平房居民區，人口密集，距離中南海3km左右<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cidjdveveb4h/status/1223805866106900480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcidjdveveb4h%2Fstatus%2F1223805866106900480&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9NOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=9af2d069\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcidjdveveb4h%2Fstatus%2F1223805866106900480&h=3112a6ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cidjdveveb4h/status/1223805866106900480</a><br />\n<br />\nVictor Du<br />\n@victordu311<br />\n加油！還剩最後三公里了！<br />\n <br />\n周得<br />\n@ABOUND5168<br />\n病毒應該有能力飄3公里，加油<br />\n <br />\nPk2020<br />\n@pangke35<br />\n哎呀真遺憾！300米就更理想了！<br />\n <br />\n念詩之王<br />\n@C0tihSRGi836onQ<br />\n中南海慌不慌啊？<br />\n <br />\n啞奴<br />\n@Shirley7407245<br />\n一片淒慘中最振奮人心的消息。<br />\n <br />\nChaseSH<br />\n@Chase49736129<br />\n終於到門口了<br />\n <br />\n羅繼松<br />\n@BZUZL6CHRktShBP<br />\n有條件最好用望遠鏡監控新建的2座醫院，別病人進去了，連屍體都沒有出來。就是陰謀<br />\n論支持者想象液體分屍，無影無蹤。<br />\n <br />\n辣條君<br />\n@reallokii<br />\n幹得漂亮！<br />\n <br />\n美國加州滅共第一軍<br />\n@chen88888899<br />\n消滅中南海的大瘟神<br />\n <br />\n柳依依<br />\n@feiyang1413<br />\n一陣風就刮過去了！<br />\n <br />\nRomEo BluE<br />\n@LinaLinaSong<br />\n風吹的猛烈些吧"},{"pid":"f1ff5c0bb951b1460ea8a2dec44158397a616c13","tid":1857642,"uid":192409,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"加油！還剩最後三公里了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s